Fix rep_memset_s to use the correct 3-argument signature for
memset_explicit as introduced in C23 and glibc 2.39+. The previous
code used a 4-argument memset_s-style call which is incompatible.

Upstream fix: https://github.com/samba-team/samba/commit/04e0fb9b2d

--- a/lib/replace/replace.c
+++ b/lib/replace/replace.c
@@ -972,7 +972,7 @@

 #if defined(HAVE_MEMSET_EXPLICIT)
-	memset_explicit(dest, destsz, ch, count);
+	memset_explicit(dest, ch, count);
 #else /* HAVE_MEMSET_EXPLICIT */
 	memset(dest, ch, count);
